lead_paragraph: Pakistan captain Misbah-ul-Haq hopes international cricket will soon return to the country as he celebrated the team's climb to the top of the test rankings by being awarded the ceremonial mace to mark the achievement on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Proud Skipper Misbah Wants Pakistan Isolation to End Soon
